---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="HealthDrop Support"
  description="Support page for HealthDrop, a one-way iPhone HealthKit export utility."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">HealthDrop</div>
    <h1>Support</h1>
    <p class="hero-lede">
      HealthDrop exports selected HealthKit data from your iPhone to a
      destination you choose.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Common Setup</span>
    <ol>
      <li>Open HealthDrop and grant HealthKit read access.</li>
      <li>Choose iCloud Drive, share sheet, or your own HTTP endpoint.</li>
      <li>Tap Export to create a seven-day JSON snapshot.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Troubleshooting</span>
    <p>
      If HealthKit data is missing, check iOS Settings and confirm HealthDrop
      has permission to read the relevant health categories. If iCloud exports
      do not appear immediately, give iCloud Drive a few minutes to sync.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <span class="section-label">Contact</span>
    <p>
      For issues or questions, contact Hankyeol Kyung through
      <a href="https://github.com/keenranger" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      or <a href="https://x.com/hankyeolkyung" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
